These are Puzzles for 5x5 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 5x5-Level-2-1::.
5 different games are played: billiard, canasta, mah-jongg, whist, bridge
The people use 5 different means of transport: bike, subway, train, skateboard, van
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: blues, funk, r&b, pop, salsa
City: edinburgh, london, san-francisco, prague, hamburg
There are 5 different favourite colors: brown, azure, pink, ivory, coral
 1. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
 2. the fan salsa is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
 3. the person driving the train is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
 4. the fan blues is the person playing bridge##1
 5. the person who likes brown is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
 6. the person traveling to prague is the fan funk##1
 7. the person who likes pink is on the left of the fan funk##1
 8. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
 9. the fan r&b is the person who likes coral##1
10. the person traveling to prague is the person playing billiard##1
11. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
12. the fan pop is the person traveling to hamburg##1
13. the fan funk is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
14. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person playing whist##1
15. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
16. the person driving the subway is between the person who likes azure and the person traveling to edinburgh##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3    |    4     |      5      |
| Game      | bridge     | billiard          | canasta   | mah-jongg | whist    |
| Transport          | train  | bike        | van | subway   | skateboard |
| Music-Genre         | blues   | funk       | pop | salsa  | r&b   |
| City   | london  | prague     | hamburg | san-francisco  | edinburgh    |
| Color         | pink | ivory | azure   | brown     | coral      |

